snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator SpongeBob SquarePants Special Pack Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into the new SpongeBob SquarePants Special Pack for PowerWash Simulator! The underwater expansion is OUT NOW on Steam, Windows, Xbox One, Xbox X|S, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5. 

Find out more about PWS: https://powerwashsimulator.com/ 

Check out the SpongeBob SquarePants Special Pack on Steam here: Https://store.steampowered.com/app/2236950/PowerWash_Simulator_SpongeBob_SquarePants_Special_Pack/

For more pressure washing goodness, subscribe to our channel!
